    pattern = re.compile(r'^[a-zA-Z0-9]+@[a-zA-Z_]+\.[a-zA-Z]{2,3}$')

        return True
    else:
        return False

- `+`: Match one or more occurrence of a space.
- `(?=\S)`: Positive lookahead to match if the following character is not a whitespace character.
